{"tid":2000584,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【重整架構？】李婉華15年加國電台節目突摺埋 去年播《榮光》遭投訴","createTime":"2020-05-04T03:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T06:35:30.000Z","uid":117837,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ea52a0bf4988d6dafec674f1f9baa9299338e35b","tid":2000584,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T03:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200503/large/1588521169_3bd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200503%2Flarge%2F1588521169_3bd4.jpg&h=97fc5111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日加拿大中文電台出現異動，李婉華在「住加女人」中宣佈壞消息，放上題為《婉華主持15年電台節目被結束》的影片，她透露：「我移民咗去溫哥華十幾年喇，一直以家庭為重，湊仔、做吓電台咁，好少同世界接觸，直至我播過《願榮光歸香港》，就出現好多傳聞話我俾人滅聲，所以我一次過講番現時狀況。」其後，李婉華直接講出壞消息，她說：「我做咗15年嘅《小心華之里》喺5月1號結束咗喇，我係一向做開一個禮拜5日嘅節目，而家變成係一個禮拜1個鐘頭嘅節目。」她指消息來得突然，亦相當難過：「始終係15年嘅感情，係好難放低。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200503/EJRDSBSKXBVSFTMX5HLM545G3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200503%2FEJRDSBSKXBVSFTMX5HLM545G3Y%2F&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWXyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=ed1d7c68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200503%2FEJRDSBSKXBVSFTMX5HLM545G3Y%2F&h=56f754cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200503/EJRDSBSKXBVSFTMX5HLM545G3Y/</a>"},{"pid":"adebc524d389ba4abdf8dd169179cba9dd16c567","tid":2000584,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T03:26:56.000Z","msg":"連登仔同我subscribe爆佢youtube like爆佢fb同follow爆佢ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nyoutube:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCSyGrmWZuI_H5wQy8z5r3kg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCSyGrmWZuI_H5wQy8z5r3kg&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWXyWRWsFhQrZK9M85